# MuseDAM Tailwind v4 Production Rules

## 1. Color Rules (MANDATORY)
All colors MUST come from globals.css variables. Never edit tailwind.config.js.

- bg-background, bg-card, text-foreground, text-muted-foreground, border-border, bg-primary, text-primary, etc.
- Arbitrary values for extra tokens:
  - hover:bg-[var(--ant-primary-5)]
  - active:bg-[var(--ant-primary-7)]
  - bg-[var(--ant-primary-1)]
  - text-[var(--ant-success-6)], bg-[var(--ant-success-1)]
  - text-[var(--ant-danger-6)], etc.
  - text-[var(--ant-warning-6)]

Strictly forbidden:
- Hard hex (`text-[#192038]`, `bg-[#3366FF]`)
- Old muse- colors
- Tailwind default grays

## 2. Spacing & Layout
- Only gap-1 (4px) to gap-12 (48px)
- All containers: flex + gap + p-4/p-6 (no m- between siblings)
- Content area: max-w-7xl mx-auto or w-full

## 3. Radius
- Button/Input: rounded-[6px]
- Card: rounded-[8px]
- Modal: rounded-[12px]
- Default: rounded-md

## 4. Typography (exact designer scale)
- Page title: text-[22px] leading-[32px] font-semibold
- Card title: text-[20px] leading-[28px] font-semibold
- Section title: text-[18px] leading-[24px] font-semibold
- Button/Label/Table header: text-[14px] leading-[22px] font-medium
- Body: text-[14px] leading-[22px]
- Helper: text-[13px] leading-[18px] text-muted-foreground